Class ConfigSources

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.j4c.config.ConfigSources

  • public final class ConfigSources
extends Object
    Class provides access to built-in ConfigSource implementations.

      • from

        @SafeVarargs
public static ConfigSources.CompositeBuilder from​(Supplier<ConfigSource>... configSources)
        Creates new instance of ConfigSources.CompositeBuilder to be used to bootstrap Composite ConfigSource instance with specified ordered list of ConfigSource instance to be used as single source of configuration.

        The builder can be initialized by ordered list config sources to be merged together. By default fallback merging strategy is used.

        Parameters:
        configSources - initial ordered list of config sources to be merged into together
        Returns:
        new composite config source builder instance initialized from config sources.
        See Also:
        ConfigSources.CompositeBuilder, ConfigSources.MergingStrategy, from(Supplier[]), from(List), load(Supplier[]), load(Config), Config.from(Supplier[]), Config.withSources(Supplier[])

      • from

        The builder can be initialized by ordered list config sources to be merged together. By default fallback merging strategy is used.

      • load

        @SafeVarargs
public static ConfigSources.CompositeBuilder load​(Supplier<ConfigSource>... metaSources)
        Creates new instance of ConfigSources.CompositeBuilder to be used to bootstrap Composite ConfigSource instance with ordered list of ConfigSource instance loaded from specified ordered list of meta configurations.

        Meta configuration contains sources property that is array of config sources. See ConfigSource.from(Config) for more information about format of meta configuration.

        The builder can be initialized by ordered list config sources to be merged together. By default fallback merging strategy is used.

        Parameters:
        metaSources - ordered list of meta sources to be used to load config sources from
        Returns:
        new composite config source builder instance initialized from meta sources.
        See Also:
        ConfigSources.CompositeBuilder, ConfigSources.MergingStrategy, from(Supplier[]), from(List), load(Supplier[]), load(Config), Config.loadSources(Supplier[]), Config.loadSourcesFrom(Supplier[])

      • load

        public static ConfigSources.CompositeBuilder load​(Config metaConfig)
        Creates new instance of ConfigSources.CompositeBuilder to be used to bootstrap Composite ConfigSource instance with ordered list of ConfigSource instance loaded from specified meta configuration.

        Meta configuration contains sources property that is array of config sources. See ConfigSource.from(Config) for more information about format of meta configuration.

        The builder can be initialized by ordered list config sources to be merged together. By default fallback merging strategy is used.

        Parameters:
        metaConfig - meta configuration to be used to load config sources from
        Returns:
        new composite config source builder instance initialized from meta config.
        See Also:
        ConfigSources.CompositeBuilder, ConfigSources.MergingStrategy, from(Supplier[]), from(List), load(Supplier[]), load(Config), Config.loadSources(Supplier[]), Config.loadSourcesFrom(Supplier[])
